nodes.text: Iko Uwais (born Qorny Uwais, February 12, 1983) is an Indonesian martial arts film actor, stuntman, fight choreographer, and martial artist. He portrayed Kanjiklub lieutenant Razoo Qin-Fee in the 2015 film Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens. He is also known for his roles in The Raid: Redemption and The Raid 2: Berandal.
